== Background
 The integration of transformer architectures has revolutionized sequential data modeling.
=== Key Components

  -  *Self-Attention:* Enables the model to weigh the significance of different words within the input sequence.
  -  _Positional Encoding:_ Injects crucial sequence order information directly into the input embeddings.
 These components act in synergy to capture long-range dependencies efficiently.

